SUMMARY:Raised By TV Events Presents: Oscars viewing party (free & all ages
	)
DTSTAMP:20260307T070429Z
DTSTART:20260315T143000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Clock-Out Lounge and Raised By TV will be hosting a live vi
	ewing of the 2026 Academy Awards at The Clock-Out Lounge this year!This is
	 a FREE EVENT open to all. Table seating is first come first serve. Sunday
	 March 15th2:30 – 9:00PM – all ages until 8pmDoors open at 2:30 for Red Ca
	rpet Coverage. The Academy Awards show starts at 4pm RAISED BY TV. Hosted 
	by Brandon Ryan\\\, Bethany Valiant and special guest friend Shane Regan w
	ill be MCing during the show and have random prizes for for best dressed a
	nd other cute things at the event and maybe more!BALLOT!!! COMING SOON **F
